{
  "stem": "16503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 396.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They clawed to the top of the wall, which there was nowhere to get to because there was just a tiny window with-- with rails covering it so that, even if you were lucky enough to crawl there, what would you do?",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would shoot you anyhow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, it was-- this rumor started to right then and there, and we got water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got water.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got-- at the other end-- you went through one end.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You got out through the another end, and they threw at you the filthy uniform-- no shoes, no hat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they marched us, and they distributed us through barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, some went there, and some went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you-- the three of us stayed together, but we were in a barrack, which was already occupied by-- by women only.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole was women.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were allotted a middle bunk for the three of us and one blanket.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were exhausted.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Let's put it this way-- just absolutely exhausted.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think I must have fallen asleep just about right away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the SS at night would come into barracks and choose young girls to be entertained.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother, as I said before, was very observant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when she saw what was supposed to be happening or imagined what was happening, she covered us with that one blanket, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The girls who were chosen came back in the morning, and they were committing suicide-- you know, walking into the barbed wire fence and, I mean, that was it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we were called out for appell, which we didn't work in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on appells, and you would stand for hours at attention in the cold, under-dressed, not fed, of course.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
